body_html:
@longchr123 why are you trying to freeze a frozen_graph?

bazel-bin/tensorflow/python/tools/freeze_graph --input_graph=/path/to/mobilenet_v1_1.0_224_frozen.pb --input_checkpoint=/path/to/mobilenet_v1_1.0_224.ckpt --output_graph=/path/to/freezed_mobilenet.pb --output_node_names=MobilenetV1/Predictions/Reshape_1 --input_binary=true

If what you want to do is to generate a new frozen graph from the mobilenet tflite&pb
(Mobilenet_1.0_224) file, try

bazel-bin/tensorflow/python/tools/freeze_graph --input_graph=/path/to/mobilenet_v1_1.0_224_eval.pbtxt --input_checkpoint=/path/to/mobilenet_v1_1.0_224.ckpt --output_graph=/path/to/freezed_mobilenet.pb --output_node_names=MobilenetV1/Predictions/Reshape_1

instead.
